# 安装


## 环境要求

> - PHP >= 7.0


## 安装

使用 [composer](http://getcomposer.org/):

```shell
$ composer require wengoooo/ymz
```

## 使用

加密
```php
$plainText = <<<EOF
{
    "start": 1561101685613,
    "interaction": {
        "keys": 0,
        "keyPressTimeIntervals": [],
        "copies": 0,
        "cuts": 0,
        "pastes": 0,
        "clicks": 0,
        "touches": 0,
        "mouseClickPositions": []
    },
    "version": "3.0.0",
    "lsUbid": "X54-6999775-5356524:1560753274",
    "timeZone": 8,
    ...
}
EOF;

echo AmzMetaData::encryptMetaData1($plainText);
```

解密
```php
$ciphertext = <<<EOF
...
EOF;

var_dump(AmzMetaData::decryptMetaData1($ciphertext));
```
